WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:30.349 align:middle line:90%


00:00:30.349 --> 00:00:32.844 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:00:32.844 --> 00:00:40.828 align:middle line:90%


00:00:40.828 --> 00:00:46.140 align:middle line:84%
>> Have you ever heard that some
people are able to eat light?

00:00:46.140 --> 00:00:48.035 align:middle line:90%
That they live on light alone?

00:00:48.035 --> 00:00:51.150 align:middle line:90%


00:00:51.150 --> 00:00:52.110 align:middle line:90%
Do you believe this?

00:00:52.110 --> 00:00:56.070 align:middle line:90%


00:00:56.070 --> 00:00:57.540 align:middle line:90%
Well, I didn't.

00:00:57.540 --> 00:01:01.710 align:middle line:10%
But by chance, I saw sometime
in the '90s this TV documentary

00:01:01.710 --> 00:01:04.250 align:middle line:10%
on the patron Saint
of Switzerland,

00:01:04.250 --> 00:01:08.940 align:middle line:10%
Nicholas of Flüe For the
last 20 years of his life,

00:01:08.940 --> 00:01:14.670 align:middle line:10%
his only nourishment was
allegedly divine light.

00:01:14.670 --> 00:01:16.830 align:middle line:84%
At the time, I never
dreamed of making a movie

00:01:16.830 --> 00:01:19.860 align:middle line:84%
about this phenomenon
some day, a project that

00:01:19.860 --> 00:01:23.260 align:middle line:84%
would span years and
take me around the world.

00:01:23.260 --> 00:01:25.170 align:middle line:90%
But this is the following story.

00:01:25.170 --> 00:01:31.074 align:middle line:90%


00:01:31.074 --> 00:01:33.534 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:01:33.534 --> 00:03:07.340 align:middle line:90%


00:03:07.340 --> 00:03:10.330 align:middle line:10%
>> Saint Nicholas of Flüe
didn't eat or drink anything

00:03:10.330 --> 00:03:13.720 align:middle line:10%
for the rest of his life.

00:03:13.720 --> 00:03:15.210 align:middle line:10%
That was roughly 20 years.

00:03:15.210 --> 00:03:18.590 align:middle line:90%


00:03:18.590 --> 00:03:21.260 align:middle line:90%
And this has been confirmed.

00:03:21.260 --> 00:03:27.272 align:middle line:84%
But of course, it
can't be explained.

00:03:27.272 --> 00:03:28.072 align:middle line:90%
That's that.

00:03:28.072 --> 00:03:35.640 align:middle line:90%


00:03:35.640 --> 00:03:39.330 align:middle line:84%
>> To be honest, I never thought
about Saint Nicholas of Flüe

00:03:39.330 --> 00:03:42.870 align:middle line:84%
again and forgot all about
the myth of being able to live

00:03:42.870 --> 00:03:47.190 align:middle line:90%
without food until I met Dieter.

00:03:47.190 --> 00:03:51.330 align:middle line:90%


00:03:51.330 --> 00:03:52.990 align:middle line:90%
>> [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH]

00:03:52.990 --> 00:03:55.230 align:middle line:84%
>> I no longer
eat physical food.

00:03:55.230 --> 00:03:57.190 align:middle line:90%
I just drink fluids.

00:03:57.190 --> 00:04:00.620 align:middle line:10%
But sometimes, I add
flavorings, a few drops

00:04:00.620 --> 00:04:04.400 align:middle line:10%
of tamari in my water
for taste or ginger.

00:04:04.400 --> 00:04:07.940 align:middle line:10%
But my only nourishment
really does come from fluids.

00:04:07.940 --> 00:04:11.240 align:middle line:10%
>> So you don't have a
calorie intake to speak of?

00:04:11.240 --> 00:04:13.010 align:middle line:10%
>> No, definitely not.

00:04:13.010 --> 00:04:15.680 align:middle line:10%
I get plenty of calories
from another level.

00:04:15.680 --> 00:04:17.779 align:middle line:84%
>> When did you start
living on light?

00:04:17.779 --> 00:04:19.310 align:middle line:90%


00:04:19.310 --> 00:04:24.780 align:middle line:90%
>> Back in 1998.

00:04:24.780 --> 00:04:27.020 align:middle line:10%
I bought that book
a long time ago.

00:04:27.020 --> 00:04:28.440 align:middle line:10%
The title looked interesting--

00:04:28.440 --> 00:04:29.780 align:middle line:10%
"Living On Light."

00:04:29.780 --> 00:04:35.320 align:middle line:10%
It seem perfectly logical to
me, because we are light beings.

00:04:35.320 --> 00:04:38.660 align:middle line:10%
People ask me, well, do
you stand in the sun,

00:04:38.660 --> 00:04:39.720 align:middle line:10%
or what do you do?

00:04:39.720 --> 00:04:44.230 align:middle line:84%
I say, no, no, it's got
nothing to do with that light.

00:04:44.230 --> 00:04:47.670 align:middle line:84%
Light is considered to be one
of the highest frequencies.

00:04:47.670 --> 00:04:52.270 align:middle line:90%


00:04:52.270 --> 00:04:55.700 align:middle line:84%
In August of 1998, I went
through that 21-day breatharian

00:04:55.700 --> 00:04:57.170 align:middle line:90%
process.

00:04:57.170 --> 00:04:59.320 align:middle line:84%
The first seven
days, they're hard.

00:04:59.320 --> 00:05:01.080 align:middle line:90%
There's no doubt about that.

00:05:01.080 --> 00:05:02.900 align:middle line:84%
You aren't allowed
to eat or drink,

00:05:02.900 --> 00:05:06.530 align:middle line:84%
not a single drop of
water can pass your lips.

00:05:06.530 --> 00:05:09.820 align:middle line:84%
After the first week, though,
you start drinking again,

00:05:09.820 --> 00:05:12.880 align:middle line:90%
clear water.

00:05:12.880 --> 00:05:16.160 align:middle line:84%
And by the end of
that 21-day process,

00:05:16.160 --> 00:05:18.090 align:middle line:84%
I really no longer
felt the need for food.

00:05:18.090 --> 00:05:21.910 align:middle line:90%


00:05:21.910 --> 00:05:24.230 align:middle line:90%
But I followed that path.

00:05:24.230 --> 00:05:27.301 align:middle line:84%
On the 50th day, I
thought to myself,

00:05:27.301 --> 00:05:29.300 align:middle line:84%
I don't know anybody who
has fasted for 50 days.

00:05:29.300 --> 00:05:31.220 align:middle line:90%
And I really don't.

00:05:31.220 --> 00:05:32.570 align:middle line:90%
That's when I knew it worked.

00:05:32.570 --> 00:05:34.700 align:middle line:84%
Gradually, your confidence
and faith increase.

00:05:34.700 --> 00:05:39.770 align:middle line:84%
Until today, I feel
secure in my practice.

00:05:39.770 --> 00:05:41.330 align:middle line:84%
I know that if I
lose everything--

00:05:41.330 --> 00:05:42.710 align:middle line:90%
absolutely everything--

00:05:42.710 --> 00:05:46.276 align:middle line:90%
I still won't need to eat.

00:05:46.276 --> 00:05:48.400 align:middle line:84%
And if at some point, I
decide it's time to change,

00:05:48.400 --> 00:05:50.890 align:middle line:90%
well, I'll change.

00:05:50.890 --> 00:05:51.960 align:middle line:90%
I can stop anytime.

00:05:51.960 --> 00:05:55.460 align:middle line:84%
Hell, I don't need
to prove a thing.

00:05:55.460 --> 00:05:57.620 align:middle line:84%
And I'd never volunteer
for medical testing.

00:05:57.620 --> 00:05:58.565 align:middle line:90%
No way.

00:05:58.565 --> 00:06:03.110 align:middle line:84%
That would go against all
my holistic principles.

00:06:03.110 --> 00:06:06.110 align:middle line:84%
When I look at doctors,
I don't see a one of them

00:06:06.110 --> 00:06:08.650 align:middle line:84%
willing to deal with this
subject, not seriously.

00:06:08.650 --> 00:06:13.730 align:middle line:90%


00:06:13.730 --> 00:06:16.850 align:middle line:84%
>> Humans need energy for
their vital processes.

00:06:16.850 --> 00:06:18.860 align:middle line:10%
If he isn't eating,
where is he getting

00:06:18.860 --> 00:06:23.810 align:middle line:10%
the energy for his heart, his
liver, or his respiration?

00:06:23.810 --> 00:06:27.350 align:middle line:84%
>> If someone tells me, I
haven't eaten for years,

00:06:27.350 --> 00:06:31.460 align:middle line:84%
and I'm still alive, one would
primarily doubt the truth

00:06:31.460 --> 00:06:32.360 align:middle line:90%
of this statement.

00:06:32.360 --> 00:06:34.910 align:middle line:90%


00:06:34.910 --> 00:06:38.270 align:middle line:10%
>> For a human to be able
to live on light is beyond

00:06:38.270 --> 00:06:40.460 align:middle line:10%
my comprehension.

00:06:40.460 --> 00:06:42.840 align:middle line:10%
Because we are not plants.

00:06:42.840 --> 00:06:44.420 align:middle line:90%
We are human beings.

00:06:44.420 --> 00:06:49.010 align:middle line:84%
And we depend on the intake of
energy in a form we are capable

00:06:49.010 --> 00:06:49.810 align:middle line:90%
of processing.

00:06:49.810 --> 00:06:52.340 align:middle line:90%


00:06:52.340 --> 00:06:56.030 align:middle line:10%
>> If this phenomenon
really existed,

00:06:56.030 --> 00:06:59.116 align:middle line:10%
people wouldn't have
to starve to death.

00:06:59.116 --> 00:07:00.740 align:middle line:10%
And there are places
in the world where

00:07:00.740 --> 00:07:03.920 align:middle line:10%
people are hungry and starving.

00:07:03.920 --> 00:07:06.920 align:middle line:90%
Why then?

00:07:06.920 --> 00:07:09.830 align:middle line:84%
>> There are no studies that
show we can last without

00:07:09.830 --> 00:07:13.340 align:middle line:84%
replenishing our energy reserves
for longer than two months.

00:07:13.340 --> 00:07:15.740 align:middle line:84%
To me, these claims
are just that--

00:07:15.740 --> 00:07:19.010 align:middle line:90%
merely unsubstantiated claims.

00:07:19.010 --> 00:07:22.070 align:middle line:10%
>> What's lacking from my
scientific standpoint is

00:07:22.070 --> 00:07:23.240 align:middle line:10%
empirical evidence.

00:07:23.240 --> 00:07:27.410 align:middle line:84%
>> And this makes
people suspicious.

00:07:27.410 --> 00:07:30.200 align:middle line:84%
>> Six years without food,
the 42-year-old Australian,

00:07:30.200 --> 00:07:34.040 align:middle line:84%
Jasmuheen, claims she hasn't
eaten food since 1993.

00:07:34.040 --> 00:07:36.650 align:middle line:90%
She lives on light and air.

00:07:36.650 --> 00:07:40.140 align:middle line:90%
Please, welcome Jasmuheen.

00:07:40.140 --> 00:07:41.510 align:middle line:90%
Thank you for coming.

00:07:41.510 --> 00:07:43.610 align:middle line:10%
You are an ambassador
of this teaching

00:07:43.610 --> 00:07:47.090 align:middle line:10%
that you yourself practice.

00:07:47.090 --> 00:07:50.880 align:middle line:84%
What is the secret
to this way of life?

00:07:50.880 --> 00:07:54.410 align:middle line:84%
>> It's the result of being
connected to a higher power.

00:07:54.410 --> 00:07:57.080 align:middle line:84%
We are nourished by
an alternative source

00:07:57.080 --> 00:08:00.290 align:middle line:90%
that Indian yogis call prana.

00:08:00.290 --> 00:08:03.410 align:middle line:84%
>> Dr. Walter Edom, internist
and head physician at the new

00:08:03.410 --> 00:08:04.820 align:middle line:90%
Wiener Privatklinik. clinic.

00:08:04.820 --> 00:08:06.890 align:middle line:90%
The claim is six years.

00:08:06.890 --> 00:08:08.420 align:middle line:90%
>> That's impossible.

00:08:08.420 --> 00:08:10.400 align:middle line:90%
>> Is this straight out fraud?

00:08:10.400 --> 00:08:13.420 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:08:13.420 --> 00:08:15.900 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:08:15.900 --> 00:08:43.679 align:middle line:90%


00:08:43.679 --> 00:08:46.950 align:middle line:84%
>> Contradictions and more
contradictions are what I find

00:08:46.950 --> 00:08:49.460 align:middle line:84%
on the internet
about breatharianism.

00:08:49.460 --> 00:08:51.690 align:middle line:90%
And I'm not getting anywhere.

00:08:51.690 --> 00:08:55.170 align:middle line:84%
But I do meet Axel on
of the internet forums.

00:08:55.170 --> 00:08:59.040 align:middle line:10%
He wants to try the 21-day
breatharian process.

00:08:59.040 --> 00:09:04.294 align:middle line:10%
And he's willing to document
the 21 days in a video diary.

00:09:04.294 --> 00:09:05.580 align:middle line:90%
>> [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH]

00:09:05.580 --> 00:09:07.774 align:middle line:84%
>> I have no idea
what's in store for me.

00:09:07.774 --> 00:09:09.940 align:middle line:10%
However, I intend to record
a diary entry every day.

00:09:09.940 --> 00:09:12.630 align:middle line:90%


00:09:12.630 --> 00:09:15.780 align:middle line:84%
Since last fall, I've known that
I would attempt this transition

00:09:15.780 --> 00:09:16.770 align:middle line:90%
process.

00:09:16.770 --> 00:09:19.200 align:middle line:90%
It was only a matter of time.

00:09:19.200 --> 00:09:23.067 align:middle line:10%
The Australian, Jasmuheen, she
suggests a three-week process.

00:09:23.067 --> 00:09:24.900 align:middle line:84%
There's no food or drink
for the first week.

00:09:24.900 --> 00:09:27.358 align:middle line:84%
And the following two weeks,
you're allowed to have fluids.

00:09:27.358 --> 00:09:29.920 align:middle line:84%
And after that, it's
living without food.

00:09:29.920 --> 00:09:31.080 align:middle line:90%
We'll see about that later.

00:09:31.080 --> 00:09:35.070 align:middle line:90%


00:09:35.070 --> 00:09:38.250 align:middle line:84%
Now, I'm about to take my last
sip of water for a whole week.

00:09:38.250 --> 00:09:43.920 align:middle line:90%


00:09:43.920 --> 00:09:45.990 align:middle line:10%
Here it is.

00:09:45.990 --> 00:09:46.790 align:middle line:10%
Cheers.

00:09:46.790 --> 00:09:50.840 align:middle line:90%


00:09:50.840 --> 00:09:56.660 align:middle line:10%
Today is March 27, 7:00 PM,
first day of the transition

00:09:56.660 --> 00:09:58.280 align:middle line:10%
process.

00:09:58.280 --> 00:10:01.220 align:middle line:10%
I feel great.

00:10:01.220 --> 00:10:02.060 align:middle line:10%
This is day three.

00:10:02.060 --> 00:10:03.300 align:middle line:10%
It's around 4:00 PM.

00:10:03.300 --> 00:10:05.980 align:middle line:10%


00:10:05.980 --> 00:10:08.880 align:middle line:10%
Yesterday, I was just too
tired to record anything,

00:10:08.880 --> 00:10:09.950 align:middle line:10%
and I was exhausted.

00:10:09.950 --> 00:10:13.870 align:middle line:10%
And I slept 14 hours
straight until this morning.

00:10:13.870 --> 00:10:15.740 align:middle line:10%
Today, my circulation's weak.

00:10:15.740 --> 00:10:16.540 align:middle line:10%
It's a little slow.

00:10:16.540 --> 00:10:25.270 align:middle line:90%


00:10:25.270 --> 00:10:26.595 align:middle line:10%
Today is March 30.

00:10:26.595 --> 00:10:28.365 align:middle line:10%
It's day fourt of the
breatharian process.

00:10:28.365 --> 00:10:29.165 align:middle line:10%
It's noon.

00:10:29.165 --> 00:10:34.244 align:middle line:90%


00:10:34.244 --> 00:10:35.910 align:middle line:84%
Feel like I'm getting
weaker and weaker.

00:10:35.910 --> 00:10:39.140 align:middle line:90%


00:10:39.140 --> 00:10:43.550 align:middle line:84%
It started yesterday
more than 24 hours ago.

00:10:43.550 --> 00:10:47.004 align:middle line:90%


00:10:47.004 --> 00:10:49.170 align:middle line:84%
That's why I'm going to
slightly modify the process.

00:10:49.170 --> 00:10:56.570 align:middle line:84%
And that means I'm going
to go ahead and start

00:10:56.570 --> 00:10:59.900 align:middle line:90%
drinking my first sip of water.

00:10:59.900 --> 00:11:01.190 align:middle line:90%
I think it makes sense.

00:11:01.190 --> 00:11:05.900 align:middle line:84%
Because first, this
isn't fun anymore.

00:11:05.900 --> 00:11:11.240 align:middle line:84%
It's starting to get tedious and
difficult. It's OK for a while,

00:11:11.240 --> 00:11:13.820 align:middle line:90%
but not for prolonged periods.

00:11:13.820 --> 00:11:15.650 align:middle line:84%
I'm a little concerned
too, because I

00:11:15.650 --> 00:11:19.170 align:middle line:90%
can't get my energy back.

00:11:19.170 --> 00:11:21.300 align:middle line:90%
Here it is.

00:11:21.300 --> 00:11:22.410 align:middle line:90%
This is my first sip.

00:11:22.410 --> 00:11:37.020 align:middle line:90%


00:11:37.020 --> 00:11:38.710 align:middle line:90%
Ah, it's like heaven.

00:11:38.710 --> 00:11:42.530 align:middle line:90%


00:11:42.530 --> 00:11:45.398 align:middle line:10%
No, this is not
light nourishment.

00:11:45.398 --> 00:11:47.920 align:middle line:10%


00:11:47.920 --> 00:11:49.730 align:middle line:10%
>> [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH]

00:11:49.730 --> 00:11:52.700 align:middle line:10%
>> As a physician, I simply
cannot recommend going without

00:11:52.700 --> 00:11:54.830 align:middle line:10%
fluids for seven days.

00:11:54.830 --> 00:11:56.780 align:middle line:10%
A lot of people could
benefit from discovering

00:11:56.780 --> 00:11:58.670 align:middle line:10%
what fasting can do
for them, but you need

00:11:58.670 --> 00:12:01.290 align:middle line:10%
to drink plenty of liquids.

00:12:01.290 --> 00:12:06.680 align:middle line:84%
This will flush the kidneys and
generally prevent health risks.

00:12:06.680 --> 00:12:08.450 align:middle line:10%
For spiritual or
religious reasons,

00:12:08.450 --> 00:12:10.280 align:middle line:10%
one might fast for long periods.

00:12:10.280 --> 00:12:12.440 align:middle line:84%
And at some point, after
three or four weeks,

00:12:12.440 --> 00:12:15.890 align:middle line:84%
one will indeed
stop losing weight.

00:12:15.890 --> 00:12:17.150 align:middle line:90%
Life feels good.

00:12:17.150 --> 00:12:19.220 align:middle line:84%
And one can then
relate better to nature

00:12:19.220 --> 00:12:22.270 align:middle line:90%
and its manifold realms.

00:12:22.270 --> 00:12:24.280 align:middle line:84%
That's the natural
course of things.

00:12:24.280 --> 00:12:27.110 align:middle line:84%
But I wouldn't advocate abruptly
cutting out food altogether

00:12:27.110 --> 00:12:29.660 align:middle line:84%
and going seven
days without fluids.

00:12:29.660 --> 00:12:32.720 align:middle line:84%
If someone has an extremely
bad diet, is full of toxins,

00:12:32.720 --> 00:12:36.230 align:middle line:84%
and has various illnesses,
fasting alone can be difficult.

00:12:36.230 --> 00:12:38.690 align:middle line:84%
And medical supervision
is necessary.

00:12:38.690 --> 00:12:41.970 align:middle line:84%
Going without water
can be very dangerous.

00:12:41.970 --> 00:12:45.880 align:middle line:90%
I strongly advise against it.

00:12:45.880 --> 00:12:47.390 align:middle line:90%
>> [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH]

00:12:47.390 --> 00:12:50.630 align:middle line:10%
>> Radical diet, the esoteric
Heidi Meyer wanted to live

00:12:50.630 --> 00:12:52.640 align:middle line:10%
on nothing but air and light.

00:12:52.640 --> 00:12:55.460 align:middle line:84%
She died eight
days later, a death

00:12:55.460 --> 00:12:57.230 align:middle line:84%
that poses many
questions, because it

00:12:57.230 --> 00:13:01.440 align:middle line:84%
happened in connection
with radical fasting.

00:13:01.440 --> 00:13:03.410 align:middle line:84%
Doctor, what happens
when one goes

00:13:03.410 --> 00:13:09.290 align:middle line:84%
without food and especially
without water for seven days?

00:13:09.290 --> 00:13:13.490 align:middle line:10%
>> Not drinking is the
more serious problem.

00:13:13.490 --> 00:13:16.680 align:middle line:10%
Our body consists
mainly of water.

00:13:16.680 --> 00:13:20.360 align:middle line:84%
If we are deprived of water for
more than three or four days,

00:13:20.360 --> 00:13:23.820 align:middle line:90%
we will, in those cases, die.

00:13:23.820 --> 00:13:28.100 align:middle line:84%
That's why not drinking
is particularly dangerous.

00:13:28.100 --> 00:13:30.980 align:middle line:10%
>> In addition to the death
of this Austrian woman,

00:13:30.980 --> 00:13:34.250 align:middle line:10%
three further cases in
connection with the 21-day

00:13:34.250 --> 00:13:37.010 align:middle line:10%
process make
international headlines.

00:13:37.010 --> 00:13:39.860 align:middle line:10%
In Germany, the kindergarten
teacher, Timo Degen,

00:13:39.860 --> 00:13:43.770 align:middle line:10%
goes into a coma after not
drinking for seven days.

00:13:43.770 --> 00:13:46.580 align:middle line:10%
He dies several weeks
later in a nursing home.

00:13:46.580 --> 00:13:50.270 align:middle line:10%
In Australia, the
53-year-old, Lani Morris,

00:13:50.270 --> 00:13:53.350 align:middle line:10%
suffers a stroke while
undergoing the process.

00:13:53.350 --> 00:13:55.850 align:middle line:10%
But the most
publicized case is that

00:13:55.850 --> 00:13:58.700 align:middle line:10%
of 40-year-old,
Verity Linn, who dies

00:13:58.700 --> 00:14:01.490 align:middle line:10%
