00:26:12.707 --> 00:26:14.540 align:middle line:84%
And we asked her if
there is anything wrong.

00:26:14.540 --> 00:26:16.415 align:middle line:84%
Nothing, she claimed to
have simply converted

00:26:16.415 --> 00:26:18.080 align:middle line:90%
to pranic feeding.

00:26:18.080 --> 00:26:20.336 align:middle line:90%
Well, that blew my mind.

00:26:20.336 --> 00:26:23.120 align:middle line:84%
It stirred me up
emotionally, got me thinking.

00:26:23.120 --> 00:26:28.010 align:middle line:84%
And then she told me
about a book by Jasmuheen.

00:26:28.010 --> 00:26:28.940 align:middle line:90%
I read it.

00:26:28.940 --> 00:26:32.170 align:middle line:84%
But I was fascinated
to say the least.

00:26:32.170 --> 00:26:35.510 align:middle line:84%
But half a year later, I
decided to put it to the test.

00:26:35.510 --> 00:26:38.315 align:middle line:84%
I undertook the ordeal of
the 21-day process myself.

00:26:38.315 --> 00:26:41.250 align:middle line:90%


00:26:41.250 --> 00:26:43.310 align:middle line:84%
