this way ever since.

00:26:43.310 --> 00:26:50.670 align:middle line:90%


00:26:50.670 --> 00:26:53.550 align:middle line:84%
I was highly skeptical about
the way the book put it.

00:26:53.550 --> 00:26:55.820 align:middle line:84%
And I never experience any
heavenly brothers working

00:26:55.820 --> 00:26:57.470 align:middle line:90%
in me, at least not directly.

00:26:57.470 --> 00:27:01.220 align:middle line:90%


00:27:01.220 --> 00:27:03.860 align:middle line:84%
