00:27:12.050 --> 00:27:13.850 align:middle line:90%
that I was no longer fasting.

00:27:13.850 --> 00:27:15.350 align:middle line:90%
It was evident.

00:27:15.350 --> 00:27:16.330 align:middle line:90%
It simply was.

00:27:16.330 --> 00:27:20.030 align:middle line:90%


00:27:20.030 --> 00:27:24.050 align:middle line:10%
It was as if I had eaten a full
meal, and I required no more.

00:27:24.050 --> 00:27:46.280 align:middle line:90%


