00:28:00.730 --> 00:28:03.560 align:middle line:84%
both in terms of
himself and in general.

00:28:03.560 --> 00:28:06.980 align:middle line:90%


00:28:06.980 --> 00:28:09.540 align:middle line:90%
>> And what are your meals like?

00:28:09.540 --> 00:28:12.690 align:middle line:84%
>> Our meals consist of me
