00:29:07.930 --> 00:29:08.930 align:middle line:90%
Where does it come from?

00:29:08.930 --> 00:29:14.640 align:middle line:90%


00:29:14.640 --> 00:29:16.890 align:middle line:10%
Normally, you think,
