00:29:28.350 --> 00:29:31.620 align:middle line:10%
The question, though, is, are
there other ways of doing this?

00:29:31.620 --> 00:29:34.770 align:middle line:90%


00:29:34.770 --> 00:29:37.050 align:middle line:90%
>> My name is Thomas Stockli.

00:29:37.050 --> 00:29:39.960 align:middle line:10%
