00:29:45.600 --> 00:29:47.370 align:middle line:10%
but great interest as well.

00:29:47.370 --> 00:29:50.032 align:middle line:10%
I find it extremely fascinating.

00:29:50.032 --> 00:29:52.490 align:middle line:10%
>> When a scientist hears about
